uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.network.process

Class NNodeBypasser

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.network.NCrawler
      • uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.network.process.NNodeBypasser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NProcessor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    NTypeNodeBypasser

    public abstract class NNodeBypasser
extends NCrawler
    Abstract processer that modifies the network-based instance representations in order to bypass particular nodes. The specification of which nodes to bypass is left to the derived class. When a node is bypassed, it is replaced in the link for which it is a value, by all nodes that are values for any links attached to the bypassed node.
